><br />\n我之前正正係做專賣呢啲個間幾日<br />\n無咩特別技能<br />\n識捉倉鼠<br />\n換木槺<br />\n日日都有個鼠打死<br />\n見到條屍唔好驚<br />\n但係啲同事西撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做唔落去"},{"pid":"1feb67919edbde5b86d21c7635a7415f0cdbba62","tid":230930,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T09:01:34.000Z","msg":"有次同條女係佢返工間寵物店度扑，比d貓狗望著好feel到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0cff8ec9d447e2bdbdc14a72e3016abe43fa84","tid":230930,"uid":29813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T00:05:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我係想做倉鼠 龍貓 兔仔嗰類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前正正係做專賣呢啲個間幾日<br />\n無咩特別技能<br />\n識捉倉鼠<br />\n換木槺<br />\n日日都有個鼠打死<br />\n見到條屍唔好驚<br />\n但係啲同事西撚到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做唔落去</blockquote><br />\n你嗰陣幾錢人工？<br />\n辛唔辛苦？<br />\n其實最介意唔係依兩樣<br />\n我最驚啲寵物打生打死<br />\n成日見啲倉鼠十幾隻係一個玻璃箱度打<br />\n好可憐咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相反兔仔嗰啲幾隻一箱又好少打<br />\n仲一隻搭住一隻咁瞓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bcb5b3a3792b55bbdba5e83fd9e3fdb78fd91f5","tid":230930,"uid":100368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T02:27:05.000Z","msg":"一定唔可以有愛心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625b7c0f97a9dbe35c6c20c345c30e410e7ef7fd","tid":230930,"uid":29813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T08:22:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定唔可以有愛心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好啦"},{"pid":"64059bf5ea39fe46e389978690e37dcaa8ae4f40","tid":230930,"uid":50073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:30:40.000Z","msg":"做過一間專賣貓狗糧同用品嘅寵物店<br />\n我個時需要嘅技能就係會撩客傾計同識基本電腦野（excel outlook photoshop之類）<br />\n普通寵物店要求應該唔會太高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6b004259f0bbbd80970b36f954beb36544699b1","tid":230930,"uid":39177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T11:49:48.000Z","msg":"做過一間唔打動物唔賣動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f445c2c632381f7b1ebb874cb1f3e17a09ac914","tid":230930,"uid":29813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:30:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做過一間唔打動物唔賣動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n賣寵物用品？"},{"pid":"328be2ed7520d1eb604a33cd6bbea7edb04d5fdf","tid":230930,"uid":29813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:30:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做過一間專賣貓狗糧同用品嘅寵物店<br />\n我個時需要嘅技能就係會撩客傾計同識基本電腦野（excel outlook photoshop之類）<br />\n普通寵物店要求應該唔會太高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人工會高啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"613b85aef60a411fddfb7cb72e2943ad5fc34631","tid":230930,"uid":11477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T03:12:01.000Z","msg":"<bl